title: Jordan Peterson at Lafayette College Comments
description:
Jordan Peterson did a Q/A at Lafayette College. It started out challenging and perhaps even hostile. Some of the questions later on were quite profitable. https://youtu.be/qT_YSPxxFJk 

Here are some introductory comments. I'm going to isolate a couple of the questions for commentary on some subsequent videos.
